export const Note = (props) => {
    const { title, body, important } = props


    return ( <
        li >
        <
        p > { title } < /p> <
        small > < time > { body } < /time></small >
        <
        button > { important ? "Important" : "Not important" } < /button> <
        /li>
    )
}
